    "title": "Analytics Accelerator showcase",
    "excerpt": "<p>California &#8211; CalHR Director of CalHR could now answer own questions about state employee data. As CalData was adapting the Analytics Accelerator for the state context, we needed testers of the updated content. The Economic Research Unit of the Financial Management Division at CalHR agreed to be a beta tester for a few of the &#8230; <a title=\"Analytics Accelerator showcase\" class=\"read-more\" href=\"https://live-digital-ca-gov.pantheonsite.io/work-with-us/analytics-accelerator/showcase/\" aria-label=\"More on Analytics Accelerator showcase\">Read more</a></p>\n",
